                            </div>
                            <div class="content-body">
                                <div class="section">
                                    <div class="section-wrap">
                                        <div class="section-head">
                                            <h4 class="section-subject" data-link-cont="anatomy">Anatomy</h4>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="section-body"> 
                                            <img src="../assets/images/components/selectButton-01-a.jpg" alt=" ">
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="section">
                                    <div class="section-wrap">
                                        <div class="section-head">
                                            <h4 class="section-subject" data-link-cont="options">Options</h4>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="section-body"> 
                                            <div class="post-list design-01">
                                                <div class="post-item">
                                                    <div class="post-wrap">
                                                        <div class="post-figure">
                                                            <img src="../assets/images/components/selectButton-02-a.jpg" alt=" ">
                                                        </div>
                                                        <div class="post-info">
                                                            <div class="post-head">
                                                                <em class="subject" data-link-cont="checkbox">Check box</em>
                                                            </div>
                                                            <div class="post-body">
                                                                <p class="para">
                                                                    사용자에게 여러 개의 옵션 목록을 제공하여 그 중<br>
                                                                    <span class="accent color-01">여러개의 값을 선택</span>할 수 있도록 하는 경우에 사용합니다.
                                                                </p>
                                                            </div>
                                                        </div>
                                                    </div>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="post-item">
                                                    <div class="post-wrap">
